{"tid":1118461,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］記者會承認犯錯，森美公開道歉！","createTime":"2019-04-21T12:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T12:36:47.000Z","uid":28938,"like":12,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1dc47ea198dcf8477f501cc105d24e4dabe27ba","tid":1118461,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:22:23.000Z","msg":"森美小儀「最想非禮女藝人」事件<br />\n<br />\n當時正於商業電台主持節目《架勢堂》的森美小儀，提出作「我最想非禮的女藝人」投票選舉。其後節目立即接獲過百宗投訴，更有婦女團體公開譴責兩位主拎公然鼓吹性暴力。二人被停職留薪兩個月，期間更不能出席任何活動或主持，作為懲戒。他們隨即在電台和網絡上道歉，並在記者會上表示節目播出後翌日已有悔意，表明是由表達方式不佳而犯錯，會負上全責。"},{"pid":"f0a18a0f62fa0cf7d111645d8b4449d39a37125a","tid":1118461,"uid":36296,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好玩？"},{"pid":"db1ffdec5a33f040005ad9a3223e6d522426e055","tid":1118461,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:30:13.000Z","msg":"對佢地好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb35f43536154b5cba85f75bafa73878a9758b3","tid":1118461,"uid":158933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:32:06.000Z","msg":"婦女團體=女權撚<br />\n如果有個問題係「最想非禮既男藝人」<br />\n撚有人會出聲"},{"pid":"cbceeca8ad41efc2763129c12f9359d05ecc19de","tid":1118461,"uid":247754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"abb35f43536154b5cba85f75bafa73878a9758b3","tid":1118461,"uid":158933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:32:06.000Z","msg":"婦女團體=女權撚<br />\n如果有個問題係「最想非禮既男藝人」<br />\n撚有人會出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"法庭都好少有非禮男人CASE"},{"pid":"a4c31309a3483a2aeeb98ce69397b420c86cabaa","tid":1118461,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"究竟點解當時會俾呢個投票出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72837f628e16a68